OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773515474
OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FThe Petrol Retailers Association (PRA)
OL,7,Fhas said "inflammatory" comments from
OL,8,Fgovernment ministers about "price
OL,9,Fgouging" and "ripping off" motorists
OL,10,Fhave caused retail staff to be abused
OL,11,Fby the public.
OL,13,FThe PRA had been due to meet with
OL,14,FChancellor Rachel Reeves on Friday,
OL,15,Fbut the association then said it had
OL,16,Fwithdrawn over concerns around the
OL,17,Fcomments.
OL,26,@pD@\OUqD@HO]qD@NOUqD@ZO]
