OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773515474
OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FHowever, the group appears to have
OL,7,Fdeleted several of its posts on X on
OL,8,Fthe issue, which had included the
OL,9,Fassociation saying it would not be
OL,10,Fattending the meeting.
OL,12,FITV News understands it will now go
OL,13,Fahead as planned.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
