OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773515474
OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FGordon Balmer, executive director of
OL,7,Fthe PRA, which represents large and
OL,8,Fsmall independent petrol retailers
OL,9,Facross the UK, said he had written to
OL,10,Fthe chancellor on Friday morning
OL,11,Fasking for the meeting to be held in
OL,12,Fprivate with no media present "to
OL,13,Fallow a conversation to explain how
OL,14,Fthe fuel markets work".
OL,26,@tD@_OUvD@VO]
