CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773515474
OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FHe said: "Recently I have heard of
OL,7,Fincidents from some of our members of
OL,8,Fretail staff being abused by members
OL,9,Fof the public, who may have been
OL,10,Fprovoked by the incorrect and
OL,11,Finflammatory language emanating from
OL,12,Fsome commentators for example use of
OL,13,Fthe terms 'rip offs' and
OL,14,F'profiteering'.
OL,26,@nD@JOU
