OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FPrime Minister Keir Starmer wrote on X
OL,7,Fon Friday afternoon: "If fuel
OL,8,Fcompanies try to rip off customers, my
OL,9,Fgovernment will step in."
OL,11,F"Rachel Reeves and Ed Miliband are
OL,12,Fbringing the bosses of the fuel
OL,13,Fcompanies in today, to make sure that
OL,14,Fcustomers aren't losing out because of
OL,15,Fthe conflict in the Middle East."
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
