OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F316A1773515474
OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FEarlier on Friday Rachel Reeves had
OL,7,Fsaid she "will not tolerate" firms
OL,8,Fexploiting uncertainty in the Middle
OL,9,FEast for excess financial gain, ahead
OL,10,Fof a meeting with energy bosses over
OL,11,F"rip-off" fuel prices.
OL,13,FThe government had already promised to
OL,14,Fintervene if companies engage in
OL,15,F"unfair" practices that would hit
OL,16,Fcustomers facing a rise in the price
OL,17,Fof home heating oil, which is not
OL,18,Fcovered by Ofgem's energy price cap.
OL,26,@wD@AOUwD@HO]
