OL,3,CMinisters' 'inflammatory' comments led
OL,4,Cto staff abuse, say petrol retail group
OL,6,FThe war in the Middle East has seen
OL,7,Foil prices spike, reaching $100 per
OL,8,Fbarrel again on Thursday and
OL,9,Fthreatening higher inflation in the UK
OL,10,Fand around the world.
OL,12,FIt follows Iran's effective blockade
OL,13,Fof the Strait of Hormuz, a vital
OL,14,Fshipping lane for oil from the Gulf.
OL,16,FSubscribe free to our weekly
OL,17,Fnewsletter for exclusive and original
OL,18,Fcoverage from ITV News. Direct to your
OL,19,Finbox every Friday morning.
